<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٢٨٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6700">أَبُو الْوَلِيدِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6739">وَهَمَّامٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4458">عِكْرِمَةَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«رَأَيْتُهُ عَبْدًا،<span class="c5"> يَعْنِي:</span> زَوْجَ بَرِيرَةَ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>